Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_io_file(25.10)                                        init_io_file(25.10)

Name
       init_io_file

Syntax
         init_io_file <file_name>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies the I/O constraint file, including path if the file is not in
       the  current  directory.  This  global  variable  replaces the previous
       rda_Input(ui_io_file) configuration file variable.

Example
              * The following command specifies the dtmf.io file in  the  cur-
                rent directory as the I/O constraint file.

                set init_io_file {dtmf.io}

Related Information
